=== Simple Distil for Wordpress ===
Author: Omar Uddin
Tags: wordpress, distil, cache, bot protection, scraping protection, CDN
Plugin link: http://uvision.co/
Requires at least: 2.6
Tested up to: 4.X
Version: 1.0
Stable tag: 1.0

== Description ==
Simple distil plugin allows you to control your cache clear for your Distil site
Just add your Auth Key, and enter the domain UUID.   

== Installation ==
This plugin follows the [standard WordPress installation method][]:

1. Upload the 'simple-distil.zip' file to the `/wp-content/plugins/` directory using wget, curl of ftp.
2. 'unzip' the 'simple-distil.zip' which will create the folder to the directory `/wp-content/plugins/simple-distil`
3. Activate the plugin through the 'Plugins' menu in WordPress
4. Configure the plugin through 'Simple Distil' submenu in the the 'Settings' section of the Wordpress admin menu
5. Add your Auth Key and UDID there.
8. Hit Save & check Distil dashboard for this project.

[standard WordPress installation method]: http://codex.wordpress.org/Managing_Plugins#Installing_Plugins

